{
  "video_id": "HI7zfpitZpo",
  "title": "Kailash Satyarthi: How to make peace? Get angry",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13111.0,
      "end_time": 18451.0,
      "text": "Today, I am going to talk about anger."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 21128.0,
      "end_time": 23130.0,
      "text": "When I was 11,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 23130.0,
      "end_time": 26462.0,
      "text": "seeing some of my friends  leaving the school"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 26462.0,
      "end_time": 30684.0,
      "text": "because their parents  could not afford textbooks"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 30684.0,
      "end_time": 33186.0,
      "text": "made me angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 35316.0,
      "end_time": 38680.0,
      "text": "When I was 27,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 38680.0,
      "end_time": 43280.0,
      "text": "hearing the plight of a desperate slave father"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 43280.0,
      "end_time": 48292.0,
      "text": "whose daughter was  about to be sold to a brothel"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 48302.0,
      "end_time": 50683.0,
      "text": "made me angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 52423.0,
      "end_time": 54763.0,
      "text": "At the age of 50,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 54763.0,
      "end_time": 59586.0,
      "text": "lying on the street, in a pool of blood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 59586.0,
      "end_time": 62532.0,
      "text": "along with my own son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 62532.0,
      "end_time": 64998.0,
      "text": "made me angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 67299.0,
      "end_time": 72484.0,
      "text": "Dear friends, for centuries we were taught anger is bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 73274.0,
      "end_time": 75486.0,
      "text": "Our parents, teachers, priests --"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 75486.0,
      "end_time": 81371.0,
      "text": "everyone taught us how to control  and suppress our anger."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 84241.0,
      "end_time": 86146.0,
      "text": "But I ask why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 87596.0,
      "end_time": 92513.0,
      "text": "Why can&#39;t we convert our anger for the larger good of society?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 92513.0,
      "end_time": 94109.0,
      "text": "Why can&#39;t we use our anger"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 94109.0,
      "end_time": 97615.0,
      "text": "to challenge and change the evils of the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 101705.0,
      "end_time": 104176.0,
      "text": "That I tried to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 106360.0,
      "end_time": 107847.0,
      "text": "Friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 109367.0,
      "end_time": 115370.0,
      "text": "most of the brightest ideas came to my mind out of anger."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 115814.0,
      "end_time": 125514.0,
      "text": "Like when I was 35 and sat  in a locked-up, tiny prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 126564.0,
      "end_time": 129670.0,
      "text": "The whole night, I was angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 129957.0,
      "end_time": 133170.0,
      "text": "But it has given birth to a new idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 133170.0,
      "end_time": 136176.0,
      "text": "But I will come to that later on."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 136176.0,
      "end_time": 143410.0,
      "text": "Let me begin with the story of how I got a name for myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 145481.0,
      "end_time": 149622.0,
      "text": "I had been a big admirer  of Mahatma Gandhi since my childhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 151320.0,
      "end_time": 156321.0,
      "text": "Gandhi fought and lead  India&#39;s freedom movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 157261.0,
      "end_time": 159299.0,
      "text": "But more importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 159299.0,
      "end_time": 166340.0,
      "text": "he taught us how to treat  the most vulnerable sections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 166340.0,
      "end_time": 170304.0,
      "text": "the most deprived people,  with dignity and respect."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 171595.0,
      "end_time": 176562.0,
      "text": "And so, when India was celebrating"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 176562.0,
      "end_time": 179829.0,
      "text": "Mahatma Gandhi&#39;s  birth centenary in 1969 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 179829.0,
      "end_time": 182117.0,
      "text": "at that time I was 15 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 182117.0,
      "end_time": 184474.0,
      "text": "an idea came to my mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 185774.0,
      "end_time": 189244.0,
      "text": "Why can&#39;t we celebrate it differently?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 189244.0,
      "end_time": 194672.0,
      "text": "I knew, as perhaps many of you might know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 194672.0,
      "end_time": 202665.0,
      "text": "that in India, a large number of people are born in the lowest segment of caste."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 204185.0,
      "end_time": 207324.0,
      "text": "And they are treated as untouchables."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 207324.0,
      "end_time": 208656.0,
      "text": "These are the people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 208656.0,
      "end_time": 213660.0,
      "text": "forget about allowing them  to go to the temples,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 213660.0,
      "end_time": 220250.0,
      "text": "they cannot even go into the houses  and shops of high-caste people."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 220250.0,
      "end_time": 225564.0,
      "text": "So I was very impressed with  the leaders of my town"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 225564.0,
      "end_time": 230102.0,
      "text": "who were speaking very highly against the caste system and untouchability"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 230102.0,
      "end_time": 232274.0,
      "text": "and talking of Gandhian ideals."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 233774.0,
      "end_time": 236944.0,
      "text": "So inspired by that, I thought, let us set an example"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 236944.0,
      "end_time": 243388.0,
      "text": "by inviting these people to eat food cooked and served"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 243389.0,
      "end_time": 246619.0,
      "text": "by the untouchable community."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 246619.0,
      "end_time": 251551.0,
      "text": "I went to some low-caste, so-called untouchable, people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 253421.0,
      "end_time": 257807.0,
      "text": "tried to convince them, but it was unthinkable for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 257807.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261760.00000000003,
      "text": "They told me, \"No, no. It&#39;s not possible. It never happened.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 263700.0,
      "end_time": 264784.0,
      "text": "I said, \"Look at these leaders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 264784.0,
      "end_time": 267221.0,
      "text": "they are so great,  they are against untouchability."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 267221.0,
      "end_time": 269911.0,
      "text": "They will come. If nobody comes,  we can set an example.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 272891.0,
      "end_time": 278751.0,
      "text": "These people thought that I was too naive."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 280161.0,
      "end_time": 282651.0,
      "text": "Finally, they were convinced."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 282651.0,
      "end_time": 288352.0,
      "text": "My friends and I took our bicycles and invited political leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 289982.0,
      "end_time": 293126.0,
      "text": "And I was so thrilled, rather, empowered"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 293126.0,
      "end_time": 297722.0,
      "text": "to see that each one of them  agreed to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 299192.0,
      "end_time": 302830.0,
      "text": "I thought, \"Great idea. We can set an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 302830.0,
      "end_time": 305711.0,
      "text": "We can bring about change in the society.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 307451.0,
      "end_time": 309400.0,
      "text": "The day has come."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 309724.0,
      "end_time": 315467.0,
      "text": "All these untouchables, three women and two men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 315467.0,
      "end_time": 318816.0,
      "text": "they agreed to come."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 319436.0,
      "end_time": 325750.0,
      "text": "I could recall that they had used  the best of their clothes."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 326475.0,
      "end_time": 328740.0,
      "text": "They brought new utensils."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 330000.0,
      "end_time": 332339.0,
      "text": "They had taken baths  hundreds of times"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 332339.0,
      "end_time": 335300.0,
      "text": "because it was unthinkable for them to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 335300.0,
      "end_time": 337944.0,
      "text": "It was the moment of change."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 339254.0,
      "end_time": 341702.0,
      "text": "They gathered. Food was cooked."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 342402.0,
      "end_time": 345000.0,
      "text": "It was 7 o&#39;clock."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 345000.0,
      "end_time": 347876.0,
      "text": "By 8 o&#39;clock, we kept on waiting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 347876.0,
      "end_time": 352857.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s not very uncommon  that the leaders become late,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 352857.0,
      "end_time": 354539.0,
      "text": "for an hour or so."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 355239.0,
      "end_time": 361921.0,
      "text": "So after 8 o&#39;clock, we took our bicycles and went to these leaders&#39; homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 361922.0,
      "end_time": 364278.0,
      "text": "just to remind them."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 366248.0,
      "end_time": 370945.0,
      "text": "One of the leader&#39;s wives told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 370945.0,
      "end_time": 375960.0,
      "text": "\"Sorry, he is having some headache, perhaps he cannot come.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 375960.0,
      "end_time": 378370.0,
      "text": "I went to another leader"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 378370.0,
      "end_time": 382970.0,
      "text": "and his wife told me,  \"Okay, you go, he will definitely join.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 383357.0,
      "end_time": 387469.0,
      "text": "So I thought that the dinner will take place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 387469.0,
      "end_time": 391952.0,
      "text": "though not at that large a scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 393352.0,
      "end_time": 399318.0,
      "text": "I went back to the venue, which was a newly built Mahatma Gandhi Park."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 400559.0,
      "end_time": 402530.0,
      "text": "It was 10 o&#39;clock."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 403483.0,
      "end_time": 406822.0,
      "text": "None of the leaders showed up."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 408132.0,
      "end_time": 410835.0,
      "text": "That made me angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 412275.0,
      "end_time": 418679.0,
      "text": "I was standing, leaning against Mahatma Gandhi&#39;s statue."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 421839.0,
      "end_time": 426310.0,
      "text": "I was emotionally drained, rather exhausted."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 428890.0,
      "end_time": 434375.0,
      "text": "Then I sat down where  the food was lying."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 437695.0,
      "end_time": 439784.0,
      "text": "I kept my emotions on hold."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 439785.0,
      "end_time": 444279.0,
      "text": "But then, when I took the first bite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 444279.0,
      "end_time": 447210.0,
      "text": "I broke down in tears."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 447210.0,
      "end_time": 452149.0,
      "text": "And suddenly I felt a hand on my shoulder."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 452149.0,
      "end_time": 458470.0,
      "text": "And it was the healing, motherly touch  of an untouchable woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 458470.0,
      "end_time": 462278.0,
      "text": "And she told me, \"Kailash, why are you crying?"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 463598.0,
      "end_time": 466110.0,
      "text": "You have done your bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 466110.0,
      "end_time": 469136.0,
      "text": "You have eaten the food cooked by untouchables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 469136.0,
      "end_time": 472127.0,
      "text": "which has never happened in our memory.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 473207.0,
      "end_time": 477789.0,
      "text": "She said, \"You won today.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 477789.0,
      "end_time": 482759.0,
      "text": "And my friends, she was right."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 484590.0,
      "end_time": 487789.0,
      "text": "I came back home, a little after midnight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 487789.0,
      "end_time": 492363.0,
      "text": "shocked to see that several  high-caste elderly people"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 492363.0,
      "end_time": 494517.0,
      "text": "were sitting in my courtyard."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 494517.0,
      "end_time": 497613.0,
      "text": "I saw my mother and  elderly women were crying"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 497613.0,
      "end_time": 502710.0,
      "text": "and they were pleading  to these elderly people"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 502710.0,
      "end_time": 505500.0,
      "text": "because they had threatened  to outcaste my whole family."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 506345.0,
      "end_time": 511477.0,
      "text": "And you know, outcasting the family is the biggest social punishment"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 511477.0,
      "end_time": 514300.0,
      "text": "one can think of."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 515981.0,
      "end_time": 520821.0,
      "text": "Somehow they agreed to punish only me, and the punishment was purification."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 520821.0,
      "end_time": 525336.0,
      "text": "That means I had to go 600 miles away from my hometown"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 525336.0,
      "end_time": 529267.0,
      "text": "to the River Ganges to take a holy dip."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 529267.0,
      "end_time": 533691.0,
      "text": "And after that, I should organize a feast for priests, 101 priests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 533691.0,
      "end_time": 537239.0,
      "text": "wash their feet and drink that water."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 538529.0,
      "end_time": 541528.0,
      "text": "It was total nonsense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 541528.0,
      "end_time": 544417.0,
      "text": "and I refused to accept that punishment."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 545267.0,
      "end_time": 547397.0,
      "text": "How did they punish me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 547397.0,
      "end_time": 553194.0,
      "text": "I was barred from entering into my own  kitchen and my own dining room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 553194.0,
      "end_time": 556246.0,
      "text": "my utensils were separated."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 556246.0,
      "end_time": 561300.0,
      "text": "But the night when I was angry, they wanted to outcaste me."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 562600.0,
      "end_time": 566633.0,
      "text": "But I decided to outcaste  the entire caste system."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 567503.0,
      "end_time": 572228.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 572988.0,
      "end_time": 578300.0,
      "text": "And that was possible because the beginning would have been"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 578300.0,
      "end_time": 580119.0,
      "text": "to change the family name, or surname,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 580119.0,
      "end_time": 583784.0,
      "text": "because in India, most of the family names are caste names."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 583784.0,
      "end_time": 586306.0,
      "text": "So I decided to drop my name."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 586306.0,
      "end_time": 592810.0,
      "text": "And then, later on, I gave  a new name to myself: Satyarthi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 592810.0,
      "end_time": 595776.0,
      "text": "that means, \"seeker of truth.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 597216.0,
      "end_time": 601248.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 601248.0,
      "end_time": 604585.0,
      "text": "And that was the beginning  of my transformative anger."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 606950.0,
      "end_time": 608704.0,
      "text": "Friends, maybe one of you can tell me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 608704.0,
      "end_time": 613530.0,
      "text": "what was I doing before becoming a children&#39;s rights activist?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 614410.0,
      "end_time": 615788.0,
      "text": "Does anybody know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 616898.0,
      "end_time": 618169.0,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 618169.0,
      "end_time": 624558.0,
      "text": "I was an engineer, an electrical engineer."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 624558.0,
      "end_time": 629662.0,
      "text": "And then I learned how the energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 629662.0,
      "end_time": 634146.0,
      "text": "of burning fire, coal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 634146.0,
      "end_time": 638250.0,
      "text": "the nuclear blast inside the chambers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 638250.0,
      "end_time": 641442.0,
      "text": "raging river currents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 641442.0,
      "end_time": 645660.0,
      "text": "fierce winds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 645660.0,
      "end_time": 650830.0,
      "text": "could be converted into the light  and lives of millions."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 650963.0,
      "end_time": 655495.0,
      "text": "I also learned how the most uncontrollable form of energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 655495.0,
      "end_time": 659970.0,
      "text": "could be harnessed for good  and making society better."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 664925.0,
      "end_time": 671692.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;ll come back to the story of when I was caught in the prison:"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 671692.0,
      "end_time": 675919.0,
      "text": "I was very happy freeing  a dozen children from slavery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 675919.0,
      "end_time": 678890.0,
      "text": "handing them over to their parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 678890.0,
      "end_time": 682780.0,
      "text": "I cannot explain my joy  when I free a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 683238.0,
      "end_time": 684428.0,
      "text": "I was so happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 685458.0,
      "end_time": 691210.0,
      "text": "But when I was waiting for my train to come back to my hometown, Delhi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 691210.0,
      "end_time": 694264.0,
      "text": "I saw that dozens of children  were arriving;"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 694264.0,
      "end_time": 697562.0,
      "text": "they were being trafficked by someone."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 697562.0,
      "end_time": 700415.0,
      "text": "I stopped them, those people."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 700415.0,
      "end_time": 702516.0,
      "text": "I complained to the police."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 702517.0,
      "end_time": 707710.0,
      "text": "So the policemen, instead of helping me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 707710.0,
      "end_time": 712773.0,
      "text": "they threw me in this small,  tiny shell, like an animal."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 713573.0,
      "end_time": 715121.0,
      "text": "And that was the night of anger"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 715121.0,
      "end_time": 718972.0,
      "text": "when one of the brightest  and biggest ideas was born."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 719632.0,
      "end_time": 725990.0,
      "text": "I thought that if I keep on freeing 10  children, and 50 more will join,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 725100.0,
      "end_time": 726560.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s not done."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 726560.0,
      "end_time": 729367.0,
      "text": "And I believed in the power of consumers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 729368.0,
      "end_time": 732852.0,
      "text": "and let me tell you that this was the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 732852.0,
      "end_time": 737968.0,
      "text": "when a campaign was launched by me or anywhere in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 737968.0,
      "end_time": 742400.0,
      "text": "to educate and sensitize the consumers"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 742410.0,
      "end_time": 746501.0,
      "text": "to create a demand for child-labor-free rugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 747691.0,
      "end_time": 751830.0,
      "text": "In Europe and America,  we have been successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 751830.0,
      "end_time": 755767.0,
      "text": "And it has resulted  in a fall in child labor"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 755768.0,
      "end_time": 759240.0,
      "text": "in South Asian countries by 80 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 759240.0,
      "end_time": 762406.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 764736.0,
      "end_time": 771396.0,
      "text": "Not only that, but this first-ever  consumer&#39;s power, or consumer&#39;s campaign"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 771397.0,
      "end_time": 775505.0,
      "text": "has grown in other countries and other industries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 775505.0,
      "end_time": 780931.0,
      "text": "maybe chocolate, maybe apparel,  maybe shoes -- it has gone beyond."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 783271.0,
      "end_time": 784823.0,
      "text": "My anger at the age of 11,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 784823.0,
      "end_time": 790175.0,
      "text": "when I realized how important education is for every child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 790176.0,
      "end_time": 797821.0,
      "text": "I got an idea to collect used books and help the poorest children."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 797821.0,
      "end_time": 801270.0,
      "text": "I created a book bank at the age of 11."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 802570.0,
      "end_time": 803813.0,
      "text": "But I did not stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 803813.0,
      "end_time": 806450.0,
      "text": "Later on, I cofounded"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 806460.0,
      "end_time": 810580.0,
      "text": "the world&#39;s single largest civil society campaign for education"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 810580.0,
      "end_time": 813571.0,
      "text": "that is the Global Campaign for Education."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 814221.0,
      "end_time": 818866.0,
      "text": "That has helped in changing  the whole thinking towards education"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 818866.0,
      "end_time": 821257.0,
      "text": "from the charity mode to the human rights mode,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 821257.0,
      "end_time": 826260.0,
      "text": "and that has concretely helped  the reduction of out-of-school children"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 826260.0,
      "end_time": 829613.0,
      "text": "by half in the last 15 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 829614.0,
      "end_time": 833693.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 835753.0,
      "end_time": 838867.0,
      "text": "My anger at the age of 27,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 838867.0,
      "end_time": 844235.0,
      "text": "to free that girl who was about to be sold to a brothel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 844235.0,
      "end_time": 849180.0,
      "text": "has given me an idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 849180.0,
      "end_time": 853271.0,
      "text": "to go for a new strategy of raid and rescue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 853271.0,
      "end_time": 856188.0,
      "text": "freeing children from slavery."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 856758.0,
      "end_time": 862614.0,
      "text": "And I am so lucky and proud to say that it is not one or 10 or 20,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 862614.0,
      "end_time": 868957.0,
      "text": "but my colleagues and I have been able to physically liberate 83,000 child slaves"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 868962.0,
      "end_time": 872930.0,
      "text": "and hand them over back to their families and mothers."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 872930.0,
      "end_time": 875452.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 877692.0,
      "end_time": 879979.0,
      "text": "I knew that we needed global policies."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 879979.0,
      "end_time": 883110.0,
      "text": "We organized the worldwide marches against child labor"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 883110.0,
      "end_time": 889730.0,
      "text": "and that has also resulted in  a new international convention"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 889730.0,
      "end_time": 893172.0,
      "text": "to protect the children who are in the worst forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 894262.0,
      "end_time": 898351.0,
      "text": "And the concrete result was that the number of child laborers globally"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 898351.0,
      "end_time": 903891.0,
      "text": "has gone down by one third  in the last 15 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 903891.0,
      "end_time": 908310.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 908311.0,
      "end_time": 911721.0,
      "text": "So, in each case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 911721.0,
      "end_time": 915510.0,
      "text": "it began from anger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 915510.0,
      "end_time": 918159.0,
      "text": "turned into an idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 918159.0,
      "end_time": 921564.0,
      "text": "and action."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 921565.0,
      "end_time": 924441.0,
      "text": "So anger, what next?"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 924441.0,
      "end_time": 926920.0,
      "text": "Idea, and --"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 926920.0,
      "end_time": 928277.0,
      "text": "Audience: Action"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 928278.0,
      "end_time": 932835.0,
      "text": "Kailash Satyarthi: Anger, idea, action. Which I tried to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 934254.0,
      "end_time": 936751.0,
      "text": "Anger is a power, anger is an energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 936751.0,
      "end_time": 939552.0,
      "text": "and the law of nature is that energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 939552.0,
      "end_time": 944795.0,
      "text": "can never be created and never  be vanished, can never be destroyed."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 944795.0,
      "end_time": 951685.0,
      "text": "So why can&#39;t the energy of anger be translated and harnessed"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 951685.0,
      "end_time": 956220.0,
      "text": "to create a better and beautiful world, a more just and equitable world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 956861.0,
      "end_time": 959341.0,
      "text": "Anger is within each one of you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 959341.0,
      "end_time": 965241.0,
      "text": "and I will share a secret for a few seconds:"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 965241.0,
      "end_time": 972795.0,
      "text": "that if we are confined in  the narrow shells of egos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 972795.0,
      "end_time": 977224.0,
      "text": "and the circles of selfishness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 977225.0,
      "end_time": 984709.0,
      "text": "then the anger will turn out to be hatred, violence, revenge, destruction."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 985539.0,
      "end_time": 988595.0,
      "text": "But if we are able to break the circles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 988595.0,
      "end_time": 994481.0,
      "text": "then the same anger could turn  into a great power."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 994481.0,
      "end_time": 998828.0,
      "text": "We can break the circles  by using our inherent compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 998828.0,
      "end_time": 1002678.0,
      "text": "and connect with the world through  compassion to make this world better."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 1002680.0,
      "end_time": 1006353.0,
      "text": "That same anger could be transformed into it."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 1006350.0,
      "end_time": 1010935.0,
      "text": "So dear friends, sisters and brothers, again, as a Nobel Laureate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 1011960.0,
      "end_time": 1014715.0,
      "text": "I am urging you to become angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 1015840.0,
      "end_time": 1018982.0,
      "text": "I am urging you to become angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 1020300.0,
      "end_time": 1024299.0,
      "text": "And the angriest among us"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 1024300.0,
      "end_time": 1031511.0,
      "text": "is the one who can transform his anger  into idea and action."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 1032440.0,
      "end_time": 1034275.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 1034280.0,
      "end_time": 1038250.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 1047109.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1050919.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson: For many years,  you&#39;ve been an inspiration to others."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 1050920.0,
      "end_time": 1054105.0,
      "text": "Who or what inspires you and why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 1054630.0,
      "end_time": 1056342.0,
      "text": "KS: Good question."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 1056340.0,
      "end_time": 1060333.0,
      "text": "Chris, let me tell you,  and that is the truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 1060330.0,
      "end_time": 1064844.0,
      "text": "each time when I free a child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 1064850.0,
      "end_time": 1069281.0,
      "text": "the child who has lost all his hope that he will ever come back to his mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 1069280.0,
      "end_time": 1073335.0,
      "text": "the first smile of freedom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 1073330.0,
      "end_time": 1075885.0,
      "text": "and the mother who has lost all hope"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 1075890.0,
      "end_time": 1082501.0,
      "text": "that the son or daughter  can ever come back and sit in her lap,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 1082500.0,
      "end_time": 1084655.0,
      "text": "they become so emotional"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 1084660.0,
      "end_time": 1089813.0,
      "text": "and the first tear of joy  rolls down on her cheek,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 1089810.0,
      "end_time": 1093155.0,
      "text": "I see the glimpse of God in it -- this is my biggest inspiration."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 1093150.0,
      "end_time": 1098316.0,
      "text": "And I am so lucky that not once, as I said before, but thousands of times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 1098320.0,
      "end_time": 1101628.0,
      "text": "I have been able to witness my God in the faces of those children"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 1101630.0,
      "end_time": 1103641.0,
      "text": "and they are my biggest inspirations."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 1103640.0,
      "end_time": 1105652.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 1105650.0,
      "end_time": 1107663.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}